  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this pilot study is to develop and implement a larger scale, multi-site stepped
      collaborative care trial that targets injured patients with presentations of Posttraumatic
      Stress Disorder (PTSD) and related comorbidity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
